# Site project only

When editing or creating files for the **kexo.io/site** project (the new front-end at `/site`):

- **Only create or modify files under the `site/` directory.**
- Do not change `server/`, `client/`, `docs/` (unless explicitly asked), or root config files.
- The main Kexo app (dashboard, API, ingest) must remain untouched.

This rule applies when the user is working in or referring to the `site/` folder or "the site" / "kexo.io/site".
